00:45:05,120 --> 00:45:08,259
Kita dahulu berteman. Jangan mengusirku seperti ini.

724
00:45:09,130 --> 00:45:10,300
Berteman?

725
00:45:10,459 --> 00:45:12,600
Kamu membuat cinta pertamaku, Bong Goo, mabuk

726
00:45:12,600 --> 00:45:14,169
